  "notes": "Records Admin API 2026-04 behavior for a successful locationDelete lifecycle with one inventory item stocked at two disposable merchant-managed locations. The public API requires locationDeactivate before locationDelete, so the scenario deactivates the target location with a destination, deletes it, then proves the deleted location no longer appears in inventoryItem.inventoryLevel(locationId:) or inventoryItem.inventoryLevels and locationsCount drops from two to one."
